{"tid":1267814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聲稱多名前警一哥出席 2頭炮撐警集會疑「流產無影」","createTime":"2019-06-30T05:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T06:02:58.000Z","uid":72009,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9fee348d0b07a361d19285ee47980e84c790a8bc","tid":1267814,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"繼「藍絲」界始祖、正義聯盟創辦人李偲嫣舉辦撐警晚會後，陸續有「愛港」組織希望自發舉辦集會，支持警察在6.12的暴力清場。網上流傳多圖，指今日（30日）有網民分別自發在金鐘政府總部、灣仔警察總部及中環海濱，舉辦撐警集會，稱要「向暴民大喝一聲」。其中聲稱在中環海濱舉行的集會，更指有多名「前一哥」出席，陣容鼎盛。惟《蘋果》到場視察，由中環天星碼頭步行至添馬公園、海濱長廊都未見有人聚集，亦看不到任何「撐警」標語或有人叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n至於政總外聲稱的撐警示威，雖然吸引到3至4間傳媒派人採訪，但同樣不見人影。3個集會中，實際上只有藍絲組織「愛護香港力量」在警察總部發起的集會有人出席，但參與人數也只有20餘人，大多為中老年人，場面冷清。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190630/59772990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F59772990&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=5bbe2bab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F59772990&h=36fd1d6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190630/59772990</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1406c5393d04f9206d7209eed232b9d14566089","tid":1267814,"uid":85629,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:35:04.000Z","msg":"廢老呃飲呃食嘉年華？"},{"pid":"f740e71a5da19e8a77e72051e24ae6c7c10eaf23","tid":1267814,"uid":177213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:35:16.000Z","msg":"緊急！！！<br />\n唔好意思借個位嚟🙇🏻&zwj;♂️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好再理「民意」喇好冇？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267806</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8ff0e0373acf7107abfd3eee9ec55311b173d9cb","tid":1267814,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2